{"word":"Silas","slug":"silas","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Silas</b> <a href=\"#/G4609\">G4609</a> <br/> Called also Silvanus.<br/> Sent to Paul, in Antioch, from Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=34'>Act 15:34</a><br/> Becomes Paul's companion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=41'>Act 15:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=19'>2Co 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Th 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=1&verse=1'>2Th 1:1</a><br/> Imprisoned with Paul in Philippi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=40'>Act 16:40</a><br/> Driven, with Paul, from Thessalonica<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=10'>Act 17:10</a><br/> Left by Paul at Berea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=14'>Act 17:14</a><br/> Rejoins Paul at Corinth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=15'>Act 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=5'>Act 18:5</a><br/> Carries Peter's epistle to Asia Minor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=12'>1Pe 5:12</a>"}]}